'''Shilin'''

[[File:10cts1879.jpg|thumb|Shilin 10 senti Iswisarland oo la isticmaali jirey 1879.]]

'''Shilin''' ([[ingiriis]]: Coin) waa jaandi wareegsan kaas oo ka samaysan [[bir]], [[dahab]], iyo [[naxaas]] leh astaamo iyo calaamado kala duwan taas oo [[dad]]ku isla garteen in wax lagu kala iibsado. Shilinka [[lacag]]tu waa shey miisaan yar oo lagu qiimeeyo qadarka alaab, badeecad, guri, dhul iyo waxyaabo kale leeyihiin. 

Hadaba [[duni|dunida maanta]] waxaa jira [[tiro]] badan oo [[lacag]] ah, wadan kasta wuxuu leeyahay lacag u gaar ah, taasi oo qiimaheedu kala sareeyo isla markaana ka sameeysan shilimaan iyo [[warqad]]o. 
Guud ahaan lacagtu waa labo nooc: mid shilin ah iyo mid warqad ka sameeysan. Shilimaantu waa qadarka ugu qiimaha hooseeya lacagta wadan leeyahay, inta badana waxa ka soo bilaabmaan [[hal|hal senti]], [[shan|shan senti]], [[toban|toban senti]], [[konton|konton senti]] iyo [[boqol|boqol senti]]. 
Boqolka senti wixii ka sareeya waxaa la isticmaalaa warqad taas oo ka bilaabanta [[kow]] ilaa [[milyan|malaayiin]]. Laakiin inta badan, lacagta dunida waxaa ugu sareeysa warqad [[kun|shan kun]] ah. 

=Taariikhda Shilinka=
[[File:BMC_06.jpg|thumb|Shilin ka mid ah Lacagtii ugu horeeysay ee dunida. Taano la isticmaali jirey [[sanad|640 sano]] ciise hortii.]]

Inkasto aanan la hubin, waxaa la sheegaa in sheeyo u eeg shilinka la isticmaali jirey [[sanad|100,000 sano]] ka hor. Laakiin waxaa la hubaa in lacagtii ugu horeeysay ay sameeyeen ganacsatadii hore ee [[beer]]aleyda ahayd ee [[ilbaxnimo]]dii [[Mesobotaamiya]] (Mesopotamia) [[wakhti]] hada laga joogo [[sanad|3,000 sano]] Ciise hortiis.  

Sidoo kale, lacagta bocoolsha (shell money) wakhtiyo hore ayaa laga isticmaali jirey [[qaarad]] [[Afrika]], [[Aasiya]], [[Ameerika]] iyo Ustareeliya. 
Shilinka shaanbadeysan ee astaamaha iyo calaamadaha leh, kaas oo ka samaysan [[dahab]] iyo [[naxaas]], waxaa la alifey intii u dhaxaysay [[sanad|650 ilaa 600]] ciise hortiis.

